00:19:42.233 --> 00:19:44.067 align:middle line:84%
They're developing
their immunity.

00:19:44.067 --> 00:19:45.800 align:middle line:84%
They're developing
their metabolism.

00:19:45.800 --> 00:19:48.167 align:middle line:84%
